llm_summary: Gate.io will delist Formation FI (FORM) from trading markets on September 9, 2024, but withdrawals will be available for one month.
Gate.io introduces Smart Arbitrage-USDT, a new Quant Fund product with a minimum subscription of 5,000 USDT, offering an estimated 30-day APR of 8.84%.
Gate.io announces the exclusive GT subscription for Mao(MAO) from Sep 13-14, 2024, with trading starting on Sep 14, 2024.
Gate.io introduces SOL Staking, offering flexible asset management with instant redemption and daily rewards, starting with just 0.1 SOL.
Gate.io will rebrand DeFi Box (BOX) to DeFi Box (DEFIBOX) and suspend related services from September 6, 2024, 06:00 UTC.
Frontier (FRONT) tokens will migrate to Self Chain (SLF) at a 1:1 ratio. Gate.io will facilitate the swap and suspend FRONT services by August 28, 2024.
